description: Project is aimed at reducing social exclusion of groups at risk by increasing their employability and (re)integrating them into labour market and society by employing and applying country wide already tested employment model (tested in EQUAL programme fr

subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: Improved instruments for integration of socially excluded people and groups at risk into labour market by introducing new training programmes and implementing them in six municipalities; fostered self-help initiatives, community activities and active participation of volunteers with a view to solve social exclusion reduction problems.
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: OUR CHOICE: Professions or Vol
